{
    "publish_date": "2012-08-22T18:56:16.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT6M40S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE REVVING]", 
            "dur": "8.756", 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Good evening, everyone.", 
            "dur": "1.145", 
            "start": "8.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A few weeks ago I bought\na Ferrari.", 
            "dur": "2.695", 
            "start": "9.901"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now why buy a Ferrari when\nyou&#39;ve, quite publicly, stated", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "16.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you don&#39;t like\nthe company?", 
            "dur": "1.455", 
            "start": "19.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, because I like\nthe cars and I miss", 
            "dur": "2.025", 
            "start": "21.191"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not driving the cars.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "23.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But really this is\nabout value.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "24.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, 599 prices in the UK\nhave dipped sharply in the", 
            "dur": "2.92", 
            "start": "26.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "past six months, and\nI just thought it", 
            "dur": "2.152", 
            "start": "29.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looked like a good punt.", 
            "dur": "1.338", 
            "start": "31.718"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, I know a car like this\nis only about 15,000 pounds", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "33.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more than the best\n575 Maranello.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "36.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now don&#39;t get me wrong, the 575\nis a lovely old thing, but", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "38.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the 599 is on a completely\ndifferent planet.", 
            "dur": "2.995", 
            "start": "42.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a fully fledged\nsupercar.", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "53.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It has a 620-horsepower\n[INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "55.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "V12 with 448-foot pounds\nof torque.", 
            "dur": "3.47", 
            "start": "57.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it weighs 1750 kilograms.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "61.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The front brakes are 398\nmillimeter carbon ceramics.", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "63.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the rear tires are\n305 section Pirellis.", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "67.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s also a GT car that will hit\n100 miles an hour in seven", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "70.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a half seconds, do over\n200 miles an hour, and--", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "73.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to me--", 
            "dur": "0.74", 
            "start": "77.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looks the absolute business\nin grigio silverstone.", 
            "dur": "3.83", 
            "start": "77.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It also uses fuel like nothing\nI&#39;ve ever owned.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "81.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think there&#39;s a hole\nin the fuel tank.", 
            "dur": "3.284", 
            "start": "84.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE REVVING]", 
            "dur": "13.136", 
            "start": "87.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But what&#39;s it like to actually\ndrive this 599?", 
            "dur": "4.49", 
            "start": "100.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pretty spectacular actually,\nI have to say.", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "105.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m a lucky swine in that I get\nto drive lots of nice cars", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "108.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on a daily basis, but this\nthing-- every time I get into", 
            "dur": "3.97", 
            "start": "111.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it I think, wow.", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "115.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I really do think, wow.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "116.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I also think at full-noise,\nin second gear,", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "118.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when it&#39;s right lit, I think\nto myself, it&#39;s got 620", 
            "dur": "4.06", 
            "start": "122.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "horsepower and yet the car\nthat&#39;s just replaced it and", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "126.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "made this the old Ferrari\nhas got another-- what?", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "128.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "120 horsepower?", 
            "dur": "1.203", 
            "start": "132.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You do think to yourself, what\ndoes that mean on the road?", 
            "dur": "2.887", 
            "start": "133.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How can you possibly use it?", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "136.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I can&#39;t use 8/10 of the\nperformance of this car", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "138.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "most of the time.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "142.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyhow, I am a journalist, and\nI have to state on the record", 
            "dur": "3.65", 
            "start": "143.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you probably never can\nhave too much power when", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "147.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re in a supercar because\nthat&#39;s what they&#39;re all about.", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "150.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is a supercar and I\nquite like owning supercars.", 
            "dur": "3.619", 
            "start": "152.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wouldn&#39;t say it&#39;s an easy car\nto drive slowly either.", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "160.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The old flappy paddle\ngearbox is not to my", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "163.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "liking, I have to say.", 
            "dur": "1.08", 
            "start": "166.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Although this one isn&#39;t annoying\nme as much as I", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "167.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "thought it might.", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "169.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At low speed you have to sort of\njust manage the throttle a", 
            "dur": "3.086", 
            "start": "171.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bit and watch out for the\nodd creep and junctions.", 
            "dur": "3.564", 
            "start": "174.922"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not as you want it.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "178.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;d love to have bought a car\nwith a stick, but in the UK,", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "179.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "apparently, none\nwere delivered.", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "182.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that meant going down the\nroute of buying one maybe in", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "184.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Germany and shipping\nit over here.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "186.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I just got a bit scared and\nthought, I won&#39;t be able", 
            "dur": "1.636", 
            "start": "187.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to sell it one day.", 
            "dur": "1.034", 
            "start": "189.532"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;m with paddles.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "190.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once you&#39;re up and running, they\nare fairly impressive and", 
            "dur": "2.567", 
            "start": "192.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the shift is fast.", 
            "dur": "1.063", 
            "start": "195.193"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And actually, you do get into\na groove, just having your", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "196.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hands on the wheel.", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "199.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[INAUDIBLE].", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "200.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there are maybe four or five\nimportant components of", 
            "dur": "4.16", 
            "start": "202.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "driving a car.", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "206.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And not having three pedals and\na gear shift to wrestle", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "207.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with, I feel I&#39;m being denied\nthat percentage of the driving", 
            "dur": "3.72", 
            "start": "209.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "experience.", 
            "dur": "0.49", 
            "start": "213.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe I&#39;m an old bastard, but\nI feel it&#39;s quite important", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "214.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I miss it.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "216.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rides pretty good.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "219.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have to say I&#39;d like to\nhave a soft [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "221.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the fast gear change, and\nyou can&#39;t separate that.", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "224.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You had to have a [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "227.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or 458 for them to\nstart doing that.", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "228.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Might have a button under there\nto be able to override", 
            "dur": "2.007", 
            "start": "230.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the function.", 
            "dur": "0.673", 
            "start": "232.623"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But other than that, my biggest\nproblem here is how am", 
            "dur": "3.585", 
            "start": "233.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I going to avoid doing too many\nmiles in it and making it", 
            "dur": "3.665", 
            "start": "236.881"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "worth about 20 pence at the\nend of my ownership.", 
            "dur": "2.771", 
            "start": "240.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s a pretty good problem\nto have, though, isn&#39;t it?", 
            "dur": "2.359", 
            "start": "243.317"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And, of course, when you switch\nall the stuff off, you", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "245.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can do this.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "248.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just lunacy.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "249.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;ll drive it a bit quicker\nnow, and I&#39;ll try and tell you", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "255.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what it&#39;s like to drive this\ncar quite quickly.", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "257.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Second gear, almost can&#39;t use\nit in the UK fully open", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "261.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s got so\nmuch [INAUDIBLE].", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "263.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got shift lights on the\nsteering wheel, which are", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "266.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quite helpful, because you can&#39;t\nlook down at the rev", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "268.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "counter when you&#39;re on.", 
            "dur": "1.645", 
            "start": "271.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Big car but the steering is\naccurate so I can get it to", 
            "dur": "3.645", 
            "start": "272.771"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where I want it to be.", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "276.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Listen to that noise.", 
            "dur": "2.455", 
            "start": "277.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, yes.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "279.821"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s very neutral.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "287.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s strange.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "289.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Even though your head tells\nyou this is a front-engine", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "290.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car, it doesn&#39;t feel that way,\nbecause it&#39;s got so much", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "292.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "traction when you just\n[INAUDIBLE].", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "295.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you smash the throttle open\nyeah, it&#39;s a problem.", 
            "dur": "2.472", 
            "start": "298.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;ll just spool up.", 
            "dur": "0.942", 
            "start": "300.828"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you feed it in it&#39;s got\nloads of traction and feels", 
            "dur": "3.916", 
            "start": "301.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "really well-balanced.", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "305.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a physically big car\nfor the roads that", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "308.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I drive it on certainly.", 
            "dur": "1.1", 
            "start": "310.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s much bigger than\nI expected it to be.", 
            "dur": "2.09", 
            "start": "311.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It feels kind of [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "313.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wide.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "315.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The 512 is a smaller car, and I\nthink that&#39;s a really clever", 
            "dur": "3.58", 
            "start": "316.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "development.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "319.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The weight, over 1700 kilograms,\nyou can&#39;t feel that", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "320.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because the car&#39;s so agile.", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "323.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got lots of managing\nsettings down here to go from", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "326.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "normal, to sport, to race.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "328.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But really when it comes down\nto it it&#39;s about dropping a", 
            "dur": "2.715", 
            "start": "330.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "gear and overtaking stuff.", 
            "dur": "4.785", 
            "start": "332.771"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, yes.", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "337.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just awesome.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "339.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The motor, it&#39;s smooth,\nit&#39;s responsive.", 
            "dur": "3.82", 
            "start": "341.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But most of all, in my head,\nit&#39;s a D2 Enzo engine for the", 
            "dur": "4.46", 
            "start": "345.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "same money as a new\n911 Porsche.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "349.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That has to make it the bargain\nof the century,", 
            "dur": "2.178", 
            "start": "352.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "doesn&#39;t it?", 
            "dur": "1.494", 
            "start": "354.844"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE REVVING]", 
            "dur": "7.548", 
            "start": "356.338"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for my money, this is\nthe best value supercar", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "363.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on sale right now.", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "366.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It isn&#39;t as pure as\nthe RS, but it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "367.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "something totally different.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "369.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s what I want from\ncar ownership, as many", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "371.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "different experiences\nas possible.", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "373.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "17.4", 
            "start": "376.736"
        }
    ], 
